Fun and exciting children’s furniture to create a delightful safe space for your child


We have invested much thought into creating vibrant, fun and exciting children’s furniture to delight children while being absolutely child safe. The BUSUNGE child’s wardrobe has soft closing doors and edges that are rounded with concealed fittings. It is deep enough to fit adult-size hangers and has adjustable shelves that can be moved as your child grows. The PÅHL desk with a shelf can be adjusted to 3 different heights to grow with your child. Kids enjoy the child-sized outdoor BUNSÖ easychair.
